title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may be nostalgic for people and places from your past. Although youre able to reach out and reconnect with some of these recollections, others are destined to remain in the realms of thought. You might drift toward sadness about what youve apparently lost while the dreamy Pisces Moon floats through your 8th House of Intimacy. But theres another way you could embrace this cosmic message with joy. Reflecting on your personal history, especially the regrettable parts, trains you to appreciate the preciousness of the present. Cherish todays moments for tomorrow they will be memories. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
